    <legibleDescription>
      <textElement>
        <![CDATA[ 
          <p>The Shelly Pro 3EM is a 3-phase energy meter.</p>
          <p>This EID is intended to be used with a MQTT broker.</p>
          <p>The EID can be used to receive data from the MQTT topic <pre>{topic_prefix}/status</pre>.
          'MQTT Control' must be enabled and 'RPC via MQTT' disabled in the firmware.</p>
        ]]>
      </textElement>
      <language>en</language>
      <uri>https://kb.shelly.cloud/knowledge-base/shelly-pro-3em</uri>
